    "The Q&A system makes it easy for users to navigate through complex and extensive research without spending hours reading and analyzing the data.",
    "Papersapp (https://www.papersapp.com/): It is an innovative AI tool assisting in the organization, discovery, connection, and writing of scientific literature.",
    "It automatically identifies and matches imported research papers with complete metadata, available supplemental data, full texts, and citations.",
    "This allows for the creation and assignment of tags, labels, and Watch folders to organize papers efficiently.",
    "It has a searchable database of nearly 130 million articles that can be accessed using its natural language processing-based discovery tool."
